summary: This is an email chain from July 7, 2020, discussing an interview of an individual who provided security for Ghislaine Maxwell on her premises. The email requests any hand-written notes from the interview to be added to the file.

events.title: Email about security interview
events.description: Email correspondence discussing an interview of an individual who provided security for Ghislaine Maxwell on her premises, with a request for hand-written notes.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain dated July 7, 2020, regarding an interview of a security individual for Ghislaine Maxwell.
The email requests any hand-written notes from the interview to be added to the file.
The security was provided on Maxwell's premises, indicating ongoing investigative activity related to her case in mid-2020.
